#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn7.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.13:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Upāsakavagga "
msgstr "2. Lay Followers "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Devahitasutta "
msgstr "13. With Devahita "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.375, sc1
msgctxt "sn7.13:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.13:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā vātehābādhiko hoti; "
msgstr "Now at that time the Buddha was afflicted by winds. "

msgctxt "sn7.13:1.3"
msgid "āyasmā ca upavāṇo bhagavato upaṭṭhāko hoti. "
msgstr "Venerable Upavāṇa was his carer. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.13:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ upavāṇaṃ āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Upavāṇa, "

msgctxt "sn7.13:1.5"
msgid "“iṅgha me tvaṃ, upavāṇa, uṇhodakaṃ jānāhī”ti. "
msgstr "“Please, Upavāṇa, find some hot water for me.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.13:1.6"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā upavāṇo bhagavato paṭissutvā nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena devahitassa brāhmaṇassa nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā tuṇhībhūto ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” replied Upavāṇa. He robed up, and, taking his bowl and robe, went to the house of the brahmin Devahita, and stood silently to one side. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.13:1.7"
msgid "Addasā kho devahito brāhmaṇo āyasmantaṃ upavāṇaṃ tuṇhībhūtaṃ ekamantaṃ ṭhitaṃ. "
msgstr "Devahita saw him standing there "

msgctxt "sn7.13:1.8"
msgid "Disvāna āyasmantaṃ upavāṇaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "and addressed him in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.175, sc2
msgctxt "sn7.13:2.1"
msgid "“Tuṇhībhūto bhavaṃ tiṭṭhaṃ, "
msgstr "“Silent stands the Master, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:2.2"
msgid "muṇḍo saṅghāṭipāruto; "
msgstr "shaven, wrapped in his outer robe. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:2.3"
msgid "Kiṃ patthayāno kiṃ esaṃ, "
msgstr "What do you want? What are you looking for? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:2.4"
msgid "kiṃ nu yācitumāgato”ti. "
msgstr "What have you come here to ask for?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.376, sc3
msgctxt "sn7.13:3.1"
msgid "“Arahaṃ sugato loke, "
msgstr "“The perfected one, the Holy One in the world, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:3.2"
msgid "vātehābādhiko muni; "
msgstr "the sage is afflicted by winds. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:3.3"
msgid "Sace uṇhodakaṃ atthi, "
msgstr "If there’s hot water, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:3.4"
msgid "munino dehi brāhmaṇa. "
msgstr "give it to the sage, brahmin. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn7.13:4.1"
msgid "Pūjito pūjaneyyānaṃ, "
msgstr "I wish to bring it to the one "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:4.2"
msgid "sakkareyyāna sakkato; "
msgstr "who is esteemed by the estimable, "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: apaceyyānaṃ → apacaneyyānaṃ (si) | apacineyyānaṃ (s1-3, km, pts2)
msgctxt "sn7.13:4.3"
msgid "Apacito apaceyyānaṃ, "
msgstr "honored by the honorable, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:4.4"
msgid "tassa icchāmi hātave”ti. "
msgstr "venerated by the venerable.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn7.13:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho devahito brāhmaṇo uṇhodakassa kājaṃ purisena gāhāpetvā phāṇitassa ca puṭaṃ āyasmato upavāṇassa pādāsi. "
msgstr "Then Devahita had a man fetch a carrying-pole with hot water. He also presented Upavāṇa with a jar of molasses. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: nhāpetvā → nahāpetvā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn7.13:5.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā upavāṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ uṇhodakena nhāpetvā uṇhodakena phāṇitaṃ āloletvā bhagavato pādāsi. "
msgstr "Then Venerable Upavāṇa went up to the Buddha and bathed him with the hot water. Then he stirred molasses into hot water and presented it to the Buddha. "

msgctxt "sn7.13:5.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavato ābādho paṭippassambhi. "
msgstr "Then the Buddha’s illness died down. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn7.13:6.1"
msgid "Atha kho devahito brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then the brahmin Devahita went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "sn7.13:6.2"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side, "

msgctxt "sn7.13:6.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho devahito brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: "
msgstr "and addressed the Buddha in verse: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.377, sc7
msgctxt "sn7.13:7.1"
msgid "“Kattha dajjā deyyadhammaṃ, "
msgstr "“Where should you give an available gift? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:7.2"
msgid "kattha dinnaṃ mahapphalaṃ; "
msgstr "Where is a gift very fruitful? "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:7.3"
msgid "Kathañhi yajamānassa, "
msgstr "How does one who is donating "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:7.4"
msgid "kathaṃ ijjhati dakkhiṇā”ti. "
msgstr "ensure the success of their religious donation?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn7.13:8.1"
msgid "“Pubbenivāsaṃ yo vedī, "
msgstr "“One who knows their past lives, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:8.2"
msgid "saggāpāyañca passati; "
msgstr "and sees heaven and places of loss, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:8.3"
msgid "Atho jātikkhayaṃ patto, "
msgstr "and has attained the ending of rebirth, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:8.4"
msgid "abhiññāvosito muni. "
msgstr "that sage has perfect insight. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "sn7.13:9.1"
msgid "Ettha dajjā deyyadhammaṃ, "
msgstr "Here you should give an available gift; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:9.2"
msgid "ettha dinnaṃ mahapphalaṃ; "
msgstr "what’s given here is very fruitful. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:9.3"
msgid "Evañhi yajamānassa, "
msgstr "That’s how a sponsor of sacrifices "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.13:9.4"
msgid "evaṃ ijjhati dakkhiṇā”ti. "
msgstr "ensures the success of their religious donation.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "sn7.13:10.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, devahito brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he had spoken, the brahmin Devahita said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn7.13:10.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama … "

msgctxt "sn7.13:10.3"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.”"

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
